### Get All Appointments
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get All Appointments with Pagination
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Appointment by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Appointment Details
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1/detalhes
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Appointments by Patient
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/paciente/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Appointments by Professional
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/profissional/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Check Professional Availability
GET {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/profissional/1/disponibilidade?dataHora=2025-09-01T14:00:00&duracao=01:00
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Create New Appointment
POST {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "pacienteId": 1,
  "profissionalId": 1,
  "tipoAgendamento": "CONSULTA",
  "dataHora": "2025-09-01T14:00:00",
  "duracao": "01:00",
  "unidadeId": 1,
  "observacoes": "Consulta de rotina",
  "planoSaudeCobertura": true
}

### Update Appointment
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "pacienteId": 1,
  "profissionalId": 1,
  "tipoAgendamento": "CONSULTA",
  "dataHora": "2025-09-01T15:00:00",
  "duracao": "01:00",
  "unidadeId": 1,
  "observacoes": "Consulta de rotina - reagendada",
  "planoSaudeCobertura": true
}

### Update Appointment Status
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "CONFIRMADO"
}

### Confirm Appointment
POST {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1/confirmar
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Mark as Completed
POST {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1/realizar
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Cancel Appointment
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/agendamentos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}